nodes.text: Mif Zinner was a male member of the Royal Naboo Security Forces who lived during the time of the Galactic Civil War.

Dialogue pertaining to Mif Zinner appeared in the directory tree files for the 2003 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided. However, he never actually appeared on the video game's live servers as a proper non-player character.
